                                 <img src="img/help/4.jpg" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="">
                                 <p>4. In the Encrypt Section, upload the file that you want to encrypt and the receiver's public key.</p>
                            </div>
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                        <div class="column">
                                 <img src="img/help/5.jpg" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="">
                                 <p>5. Download your encrypted .zip file here.</p>
                            </div>
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                        <div class="column">
                                 <img src="img/help/6.jpg" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="">
                                 <p>6. In the Decrypt Section, upload the encrypted files .zip that you downloaded and your private key to decrypt the files.</p>
                            </div>
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                        <div class="column">
                                 <img src="img/help/7.jpg" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="">
                                 <p>7. Download your decrypted file from here.</p>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>